SaveToDataset(boolean)

Overloaded. Copies all the Fields' content to the Dataset then 'loops' to Nested Sub Records and Nested Sub Recordsets 2018-0058 Save to Dataset salva i dati del Record direttamente su un dataset mappato dal campo DBField Dataset is not exactly a TDataset Class, it is, instead, a IJanuaDBDataset Object that is a collection of TDataset and Procedures, scripts or Delphi functions to store Data into the target Database that can be a simple file, a remote location, a SQL database or NoSql Database or ... whatever ...
